long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
⚙️ 🛃Developed an extension that utilises services to enhance your reading experience since was sick of interruptions on websites.

👫 ⤴The active tab or link URL is sent to a third-party service by this extension. They then work their magic to clear the clutter, making the page easier to read.

🙆 🔑Any suggestions or remarks? Do you want to insult the developer?

🚿 🆙 Disclaimer: This extension utilizes third-party services to clean up website clutter. At the moment, it utilizes the services of:

🎤 Outline TTS
🖨 Print Friendly
🇨🇩 Good
⚫ Darkread
